SP_DELETE-OPENWEBUI()
{
: << DOCUMENTATION

This plugin allows deletion of an Ollama installation.

Action:  DELETE-OLLAMA
Confirm: Y

DOCUMENTATION

  GetVar -pattern "confirm" -name "CONFIRM" -default "N" # Task will pause for (x) seconds

  Task "obrar REMOVE-OPENWEBUI -f"
  Task "obrar REMOVE-OLLAMA -f"

 }